<HEAD>With PM-US-Soviet Collisions Bjt</HEAD>
<DATELINE>HONOLULU (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A U.S. Coast Guard cutter escorted a Soviet
research vessel into Hilo Harbor so a crew member could be treated
